725349f-a.title: Queens: 45th Avenue - Queens Boulevard
725349f-a.text:
Forty-fifth Ave., north side, east from its intersection with
Queens Boulevard and 70th Street. Tracks in the foreground are on
Queens Boulevard. This view shows in order just beyond white fence
at the left foreground the following: Kugel's saloon; Peter Rimbold's
house, 1873-1891 (white house); adjoining it is that of J. Knauer,
1873; beyond it is that of H. Eahrs, 1873 7 (flat roof) and then that
of one McGregor, 1873.
February 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
